channel.title: RSCD v25 bugs
channel.description: What known bugs exist in RSCD v25 (the leaked version) ? I've been trying to hack together my own solution but it's a lot of work. To be honest I'm probably better off starting with the content-complete RSCD v25 and making my improvements to it instead, rather than trying to do it the other way around.
